reviewText: For fans of Hentei, this is a series to grab! If you must have story, plot, and rich charactor development, stop and watch Sex and the City. If you're a fan of stylish animation, and plenty of wanten sex, don;t walk....run and grab this title!

it's a little misleading if your only after girl girl scenes this may not be the best thing for you because there is male nudity and some other gross stuff too but if you don't mind then this is recomended.
